title: Coronavirus: Prince Charles tests positive for COVID-19

content:
Prince Charles has tested positive for the coronavirus, Clarence House says.The 71-year-old is displaying mild symptoms, but is otherwise in “good health”, it said.
The Duchess of Cornwall, 72, has also been tested but does not have the virus.
